<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>パート <span>1</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="優しい視点を育む"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.84.AA.E3.81.97.E3.81.84.E8.A6.96.E7.82.B9.E3.82.92.E8.82.B2.E3.82.80"><div class="method_label">パート 1 の 3:</div>優しい視点を育む</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_1" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-00">
<a name="step_1_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Be-Kind-Step-1.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Be Kind Step 1というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f9/Be-Kind-Step-1.jpg/v4-728px-Be-Kind-Step-1.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0777551d88852a879f92c90bc990332b" onload="WH.performance.clearMarks('image1_rendered'); WH.performance.mark('image1_rendered');" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f9/Be-Kind-Step-1.jpg/v4-460px-Be-Kind-Step-1.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0777551d88852a879f92c90bc990332b')</script>
